# URLs that lychee should skip entirely.
# Patterns here are Rust regex against the full URL.

# Internal / dev-only domains that won't resolve publicly yet.
^https?://(localhost|127\.0\.0\.1)
^https?://([a-z0-9-]+\.)?example\.(com|org|net)
^https?://your-domain\.

# Google Search Central help pages (often 302-chain and rate-limit aggressive bots)
^https://developers\.google\.com/search/docs

# orcid placeholder (when ORCID is registered we'll remove this)
^https://orcid\.org/0000-0000-0000-0000
